Enum Class Direction

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Direction>
me.squidxtv.frameui.math.Direction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Direction>, Constable
public enum Direction extends Enum<Direction>
The Direction enum represents the four possible cardinal directions in a Minecraft world.
